{"tid":2415819,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印軍租以色列無人機監控邊防","createTime":"2021-02-20T14:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T14:56:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e140f3194759cec68824a84cde5db9e09ba6e7d7","tid":2415819,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210220/4F45NNOGKFAGXOIVX6IUKWZC7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210220%2F4F45NNOGKFAGXOIVX6IUKWZC7Y%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=5091389d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210220%2F4F45NNOGKFAGXOIVX6IUKWZC7Y%2F&h=8bfee59d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210220/4F45NNOGKFAGXOIVX6IUKWZC7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n印軍租以色列無人機監控邊防<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iKzfKXATUaWG_MjYedP8tBxOlcQ=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YWQBCYDMVRH5PDMP5G4XNXAGT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiKzfKXATUaWG_MjYedP8tBxOlcQ%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYWQBCYDMVRH5PDMP5G4XNXAGT4.jpg&h=32e11457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蒼鷺無人機可配搭武器。<br />\n<br />\n印媒《歐亞時報》網站報道，印軍以2億美元（15億港元）從以色列租賃了四架「蒼鷺TP」無人機，用來監視拉達克東部中印邊境地區情況。但印度陸軍和國防部拒絕評論。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中印衝突 四兵陣亡獲追封  官媒記載：三人衝入「石頭雨」救團長戰死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為期三年總額15億<br />\n<br />\n印度武裝部隊長期以來一直使用以色列無人機執行監視任務，目前印度空軍約有10架「蒼鷺TP」無人機，今次是印度陸軍首次裝備及使用這款無人機。印媒稱這項合同的價值約為2億美元，租期為三年，到期後還可以選擇繼續延長兩年。<br />\n<br />\n印度陸軍此前是使用「搜索者」無人機，該無人機最高僅能飛6,100米，但中印邊境位處喜馬拉雅山脈一帶，部份山峯超過5,000米，對「搜索者」無人機屬挑戰。<span class=\"orange\">相反蒼鷺TP最高可在1萬米高空高中，速度更快，更特別是部份型號更可搭配武器，進行高空攻擊。</span>印度陸軍北部戰區司令Joshi稱，目前中印兩國都在撤軍，印度正使用無人機聯控整個撤軍過程。印度目前與美、日及澳洲關係密切，四國外長前天舉行電話會談，明言對於中國海警局通過可動武的海警法深感憂慮，一致反對中國企圖片面改變現狀。《歐亞時報》"},{"pid":"abc0e1cc390cde444ad0cd5fb57eb1549ce862ea","tid":2415819,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47114843a787d21fdd8f54408ebf212d1204906e","tid":2415819,"uid":361821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以裝忍者飛彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2e009e85bcd3a34f6bf53d32da4743f61d37d6","tid":2415819,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"又可以幫解放軍增加多d英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960e39851aea1f6cbdefd1cf5fa2cf5245f22c8c","tid":2415819,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"平價版mq9"}]}